<span class="line"><span>│   │       ├── DemoApplication.java</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   │       ├── controller/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   │       ├── service/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   │       ├── mapper/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   │       └── entity/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│   └── resources/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│       ├── application.yml</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>│       └── static/</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>└── test/</span></span></code></pre>
